1. Installations
Install Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributable by the link below // Cai dat Microsoft Visual C++
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/windows/latest-supported-vc-redist?view=msvc-170
Install python with version >= 3.14 // Cai dat python 3.14 hoac cao hon
Install Viber desktop // Cai dat Viber

2. Ensure pip is available by executing command:  // Cai dat pip neu chua co hoac cap nhat pip ban moi nhat
`python -m pip install --upgrade pip`

3. Create virtual environment by executing command: // Tao moi truong ao
`python -m venv venv`

4. Install dependencies // Cai dat thu vien can thiet cho chuong trinh
- Open project directory
- Double clicks on `install_dependencies.bat` to install all dependencies (libraries)

5. Execute the bot // Chay bot
- Before executing bot, ensure the viber is closed and reopen again
- Double clicks on `run.bat`